I like how you think, Todd.  :-)

I don&#39;t know the history behind the design decision to use static  
methods in Assert, but I&#39;d love to know.

For lack of a better way to log each assertion, I can only offer one  
suggestion:  You have the source.  It wouldn&#39;t bother me to roll a  
custom JUnit and distribute it on a project, as long as it didn&#39;t  
fundamentally change how folks expect to use it.

Mike

